# 4_loop_on_command

loop do
  puts 'Should I stop looping?'
  answer = gets.chomp

  if answer == "yes"
    break
  end

  puts "Enter 'yes' to stop."
  
end


=begin

Create an if statement and set the condition to
answer == "yes" then break

after solution lookup
add additional instructions to stop the loop
if desired answer is not submitted.

=end
